ArrayList ek dynamic array hota hai jo automatically size increase/decrease kar sakta hai.
Dynamic size (fixed nahi hota)
Index based access (fast retrieval – O(1))
Duplicate values allow karta hai
Maintains insertion order
Non-synchronized (thread-safe nahi hota)
